<title>Questions</title>
<exercise id="fs-idm248231824">
<problem id="fs-idm240874736">
<para id="fs-idm265629136"><link class="lo-reference" document="m67864"/>Name two situations where cash would be remitted to a customer from a retailer after purchase.</para>
